&lt;p&gt;Tecovas is passionate about offering an incredible customer experience for first-time boot buyers and western enthusiasts alike! This shop-in-shop location will be located in the Bass Pro Shops in Sayreville, NJ. We&#39;re looking for a Full-Time Assistant Store Manager to join our team who will bring an immersive Tecovas retail experience to Bass Pro Shops’ customers and help lead a profitable, customer-centric store. As a Tecovas ASM, you are a key part of the engine that keeps the store running — supporting the Store Manager in developing a high-performing team, owning an Area of Responsibility, and delivering an exceptional in-store experience day in and day out. &amp;nbsp;You will support product flow, uphold visual standards, and apply your leadership and merchant skills to create a store environment that is unmistakably Tecovas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CUSTOMER EXPERIENCE&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Cultivates genuine customer connections and acts as a brand ambassador&lt;br&gt;- Maintains active floor presence, managing multiple customer interactions simultaneously&lt;br&gt;- Delivers high-quality product services (branding, debossing, boot stretching, brim shaping, boot shines)&lt;br&gt;- Leads professional and gracious resolutions for customer returns, exchanges, or warranty inquiries.&lt;br&gt;- Leverages OMNI Channel tools and processes to better serve the customer&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;LEADERSHIP &amp;amp; TEAM MANAGEMENT&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Sets the tone and energy for the day, building team morale and a people-first culture&lt;br&gt;- Supports the Store Manager in recruiting, hiring, and retaining top talent&lt;br&gt;- Owns an assigned Area of Responsibility (AOR) and drives accountability within it&lt;br&gt;- Fosters strong communication and teamwork across operational, visual, and customer priorities&lt;br&gt;- Provides real-time feedback, coaching, and training; escalates issues as needed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;TRAINING &amp;amp; DEVELOPMENT&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Delivers in-person onboarding training alongside e-learning for all new hires&lt;br&gt;- Ensures timely completion of training paths and compliance with established policies&lt;br&gt;- Facilitates ongoing training for new products, services, and initiatives&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Work closely with store leadership and HQ partners to facilitate and organize ongoing training in store locations, including training for new products and services&lt;br&gt;- Attend regular training meetings to ensure understanding of necessary information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VISUAL MERCHANDISING&lt;/p&gt;
