&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;BUSINESS OPERATIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Executes store opening and closing procedures&lt;br&gt;- Monitors daily communications across email, Slack, and Zipline&lt;br&gt;- Sets up daily tools (hitching posts, zone charts) and coordinates team break coverage&lt;br&gt;- Manages Amazon and supply orders; maintains an organized backroom&lt;br&gt;- Updates the sales whiteboard weekly and speaks confidently to store performance&lt;br&gt;- Ensures compliance with shipments, transfers, restock, and Loss Prevention standards&lt;br&gt;- Demonstrates flexibility across all functional areas — visual, operations, and beyond&lt;/p&gt;
