&lt;p&gt;- 3+ years retail management experience&lt;br&gt;- People-first mentality with a positive attitude and ability to build team morale&lt;br&gt;- Ability to handle difficult situations with grace and professionalism&lt;br&gt;- Strong merchant skills and a history of

