&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Lead Change &amp;amp; Innovation: lead and support new ideas and initiatives to evolve the retail experience for the customer; drive sales and provide a store experience unique to Tecovas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
